  "text": "Both interview transcripts and field notes were analyzed using qualitative methods described in [CITATION_1] . Interview analysis consisted of reading and rereading of transcripts by two of the authors. We first coded responses into categories corresponding to the primary foci of the study: audience awareness and interaction. While the interviews covered a range of topics, we focused our analyses here on issues of instructor-student interaction and attention.",
